OL,3,CAsda workers demand equal pay in
OL,4,Clandmark court case
OL,6,FOver 60,000 Asda workers are launching
OL,7,Fthe largest ever equal pay claim in
OL,8,Fwhich female retail workers say they
OL,9,Fare paid less than Asda's male
OL,10,Fwarehouse staff.
OL,12,FWorkers from supermarket giant Asda
OL,13,Fwill stage demonstrations on Monday to
OL,14,Fmark the start of an equal pay claim.
OL,16,FThe GMB said the case involves more
OL,17,Fthan 60,000 workers, calling it the
OL,18,Fbiggest ever in the private sector.
