OL,3,CAsda workers demand equal pay in
OL,4,Clandmark court case
OL,6,FWorkers will demonstrate outside the
OL,7,FTUC Congress in Brighton and in
OL,8,FManchester where the case will be held.
OL,10,FThe GMB said the case is expected to
OL,11,Flast three months.
OL,13,FThe union is arguing that the
OL,14,Fpredominantly female retail workforce
OL,15,Fis paid up to #3.74 an hour less than
OL,16,Fthe mainly male warehouse workforce.
OL,18,FClaimants will say that retail work is
OL,19,Fof equal value to the company as
OL,20,Fwarehouse work.
